    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="862717175">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-862717175" class="vote-count">2</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-862717175" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="862717175">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/manning/">Tensor Eigen</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2015-04-07</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">钱穆对朱熹的理解大体到位，唯言语上过誉。似是朱子学的类书，可做朱熹全集的津梁，与陈荣捷的朱子研究合参，大体尽了。但对朱熹哲学无发明，为其弊。是读全集的好注解。与牟宗三的争执也隐见。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="714849124">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-714849124" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-714849124" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="714849124">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Schicksalslied/">打铁</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2013-08-13</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">不论就纯思想还是就思想史，此书皆足以为典范。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1170828224">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1170828224" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1170828224" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1170828224">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/3563379/">四藏居士</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2017-03-29</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">朱熹是很了不起，但也没有到钱穆所说远超清人的程度，过于贬损朱熹不对，过于赞扬又走向另一极端，随便发议论时有领悟语和写成文章之间的难易稍写过文章的人都知道。钱穆注语如同佛头着粪，尽可跳过，惟是书是朱熹著作的类书提纲，纲要又是提纲的提纲。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="985254939">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-985254939" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-985254939" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="985254939">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/yanwen101/">炎文V</a>
                    <span>2015-12-08</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">2013年阅</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="677906254">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-677906254" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-677906254" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="677906254">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1289017/">索思爵士</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2013-05-08</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">世传朱子学问不以大块文章，皆日常话语点滴功夫，然而每发一言用心深邃，一生所积卷帙浩繁，凡夫初涉不能阅尽，亦不易窥其门径领会内在系统；宾四先生此书举朱子之大要，从彼思想、学术、行事逐条辑成门类，学案之体细辨入微，朱子极重名辞义界，命辞有差，即见解有差，非如此不能体现大哲之全面；当知若无此疏通整理，则先生后学所撰朱子学专著，可否见诸笔墨似难肯定；此番草草读去略未尽意，如朱子之体大，宾四先生之精深，此书必当一读再读</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

